leads.lead_text: Leaves ovate-oblong, strongly reticulate-veined; exterior of corolla purplish; follicles with spines to c. 5 mm long
Leaves linear-lanceolate or lanceolate, not strongly veined; exterior of corolla white; follicles with spines to c. 10 mm long
Follicle ovoid, slightly falcate, with a clear beak at apex
Follicle globose or subglobose, not falcate, without a beak or beak inconspicuous at apex
